for item in index1:
    assert item in index2
for item in index2:
    assert item in index1
assert 1 in index2
assert len(index1) == 3
index1.add(4)
assert len(index1) == 4
index1.discard(4)
assert index1.index == [1, 2, 3]
index1.update([4, 5])
assert index1.index == [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
index1.difference_update([4, 5])
assert index1.index == [1, 2, 3]
assert len(index1.random_sampling(0.66)) == 2
